302
00:18:04,247 --> 00:18:08,407
The victor, thus far, has
demolished all who oppose him.

303
00:18:08,846 --> 00:18:12,325
The surviving champion,
your favourite and mine,

304
00:18:12,805 --> 00:18:14,245
the Red Knight.

305
00:18:19,764 --> 00:18:21,283
At the other end,

306
00:18:21,483 --> 00:18:23,483
