00:21:29,596 --> 00:21:31,195
What are you leading up to?

368
00:21:31,596 --> 00:21:33,715
Nothing, dear.

369
00:21:34,715 --> 00:21:37,303
I just thought that
perhaps you could talk

370
00:21:37,304 --> 00:21:39,833
things over with that
nice Mr. Whitfield.

