402
00:25:26,296 --> 00:25:30,735
so you may no longer
use me as a cat's paw.

403
00:25:30,775 --> 00:25:34,814
I bid you farewell, more
in sorrow than in anger.

404
00:25:34,894 --> 00:25:37,613
Please do not send us any
more fruit for Christmas.

