446
00:27:51,580 --> 00:27:54,419
I'll tear his chicken-livered
gizzard to pieces.

447
00:27:55,538 --> 00:27:57,818
I'll stomp him silly. I'll
take this letter knife

448
00:27:57,898 --> 00:28:00,378
and I'll stab that kid in
his ungrateful breastbone.

449
00:28:01,258 --> 00:28:05,536
You know me, Millicent.
Normally I'm a kindly fellow.

450
00:28:05,816 --> 00:28:08,656
But when I get
crossed, I go bananas.

451
00:28:10,215 --> 00:28:12,374
Yes? Oh.

452
00:28:13,094 --> 00:28:14,174
It's your nephew.

453
00:28:14,254 --> 00:28:15,334
Willoughby?

454
00:28:15,894 --> 00:28:17,133
Where are you?

455
00:28:17,493 --> 00:28:18,733
Oh, hi, Uncle.

456
00:28:18,972 --> 00:28:21,772
I thought I'd save time
